{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_02_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 お姉さんらしい振る舞い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう。千紗は今からレッスンか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning. Do you have a lesson from now‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、時間が空いたので自主練をしようと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have some free time‚ so I was going to practice my own a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "この間、麻奈さんのバースデーパーティーをして\n改めて凄い人だったんだって実感したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the birthday party for Mana-san‚\nI was reminded of just how amazing she is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "それで少しでも麻奈さんに近づけたらと思って\n自主練を始めてみたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be just like her! Or as close as I can get.\nSo I’ve started my own training routine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私なんかが麻奈さんみたいになろうなんて\nおこがましいですよね……すみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s silly of me‚ isn’t it.\nTo think I could ever be like Mana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうでもないさ。向上心を持つのはいいことだ\nそんな頑張る千紗に仕事のオファーが来てるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not silly‚ no. It’s good to want to improve yourself.\nAll your hard work has got you a new job offer‚ in fact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "新しいお仕事ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "テレビ番組の企画で、星見プロから四人を選抜して\n教会っぽい所で一夜限りの特別ライブをやるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A TV show is going to pick four girls from Hoshimi Productions\nand put on a special one-night live in a church-like venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "その選抜メンバーに私が選ばれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’ve been selected as one of the four?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、サニピのみんなと別れて活動するなんて……\nちゃんと出来るか不安です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not sure about working away from Sunny Peace.\nDo you think I can do it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "最近の千紗はラジオとか一人でやる仕事も増えてきて\nアイドルとして着実に成長している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve had a lot more solo work recently‚ such as being on the radio.\nYou’re really coming into your own as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "大変な企画だが、今の千紗ならやり遂げられるはずだ\n俺はそう信じてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a big job‚ but I know you can handle it.\nI believe in you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n分かりました、が、頑張ります……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nOkay! I-I’ll do my best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "それで、私以外のメンバーはもう決まってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have the other three been picked as well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今回は神聖な場所が似合う少女達ということで\n星見プロの年少組でやりたいというオファーなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They want the youngest girls from Hoshimi Productions\nsuited to the holy setting and atmosphere they’re going for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "年少組……私達の中で一番年下なのは\n十四歳のこころちゃんと十五歳のすみれちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The youngest? The girls younger than me would be\n14 year old Kokoro-chan and 15 year old Sumire-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それに十五歳のすずと、十七歳の千紗を含めた四人が\n今回限りのユニットのメンバーだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Suzu‚ who’s 15‚ and you Chisa‚ at 17.\nYou are the four members for this special one-off team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも雫ちゃんは十六歳で私より年下じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are? But Shizuku is younger than me‚ at 16――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、じゃあ早速、具体的な仕事の話をしようか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay! Let’s get right into the details!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（ごめん、千紗は小動物っぽいイメージだから）\n（きっと年下だと勘違いされてオファーされたんだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sorry‚ Chisa‚ you’ve got a small‚ cute look to you.)\n(I’m sure they made the offer thinking you’re a bit younger!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん……\nお話があるんですけどいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-san…\nDo you have a moment to talk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5333333351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、千紗。何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s up‚ Chisa? Something the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "実は例のユニットのメンバー四人で集まって\nこれから初レッスンをするんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The four members for the one-off team have gathered‚\nand we’re about to have our first lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "私がメンバーの中で一番年上だから、年上らしく\n頼りになるお姉さんにならなきゃって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the oldest among us‚ so I need to act my age\nand be the onee-chan for the other girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "でも年上らしい振る舞いって\nどうしたらいいのか分からなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The problem is how to act\nas a onee-chan would…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、教えて下さい\nお姉さんらしくするにはどうしたらいいんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ please tell me.\nWhat should I do? How should I act?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "千紗がお姉さんらしく……それは難問だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm. That’s a tough one‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
